version_description:
* Level cap has been increased to level 30! Stop catnapping and earn those extra levels meow!
* Great news! We've released three adorable new kitties for you to discover! Meet Scooper Skippy, Kale the Salad Maker, and grab a drink at Jasmine's Juice Bar!
* Numerous new quests have been added to unlock the Ice Cream Stand, Salad Bar, Juice Bar, Lemon Tree and Orange Tree!
* Improved load times! Get in the game to play with your Kitties even faster than ever.
* New and improved animations for Hoodini, the Sleepy Owl! Also, fog clouds are now 20% fluffier!
* Grab some bait and head on over to Siggi's Fish Pond. We made a few tweaks to Fishing in order to make it more PAW-some!
* We got great feedback from everyone and have squashed many bugs that were causing our players to hiss.

Have fun with Kitty City iMessage STICKERS!
Visit Charity’s building to create a club!
Invite your friends to join and play along with you!
Purr and meow with your friends via chat!
Choose your own path by adding roads
Feeding your furry friends has an all new look and bonus!
More levels and more cats and more quests!
Maggie, Fritz, Samantha, Bob and Mugs are ready to produce even more meowntains of items for you.
Numerous new quests have been added to unlock the additional buildings.
